    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>General term for wood from several species of trees, characterized by being very hard, yellowish brown in color, and having a satiny luster; used especially for fine woodworking and tools.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
